overview: Wasima and Jessica, her granddaughter, had a fight. After Jessica slammed the door and walked out, she was cursed to become a stingray. Wasima and Jessica (already a stingray) were interviewed on TV and invited as guests. Two years later, a mysterious figure is waiting for Mrs. Wasima at her house.
title: Film Ikan Pari (Dunia Tanpa Hoax)
